Title: MyDock internals
Description: MyDock internals is a collection of code for working with Silverlight from unmanaged code.
HomeWiki:
MyDock internals is a collection of helper code for working with Silverlight in C++ which I created while developing MyDock. More information on MyDock is located on http://alexezh.googlepages.com

PathConvert.js

Converts path mini language to geometry objects

Delegate.h

Helper class for event handlers for SL events

Disp.zip

Contains helpers for accessing SL object model and an updated version of Delegates.h
